questions.quote: Okay, let's see, we got strained peas, strained carrots... Ooh! Strained plums. We haven't tried that yet.
I'm sorry it didn't work out between you and me, or you and me. Drew was very disappointed.
No! Come on let's-One more time! One final push! Ready? 1...2...3!
Ross, Rachel doesn't know that you wanna get back together. If she did, she might feel differently. She might not even go.
